  "lyrics": "All I fear, all I fear, all I knew inside my own little dream In the mirror's gaze, a haunting sight Reflections of the whispers of a dead night Fear of, fear of myself, fear of myself Yeah, the mask once tied to hide the truth Unraveling thoughts lost in my youth The battle within and the constant strife Afraid of what's been losing my life Be yourself, the untamed within A labyrinth of doubt that starts to spin In the depths of your soul A silent cry makes you grow Cause fear is in us all You gotta work past it as you grow old My friend, we've all felt this way We all deal with it in our own way Cause the sirens keep going off inside our minds Embrace yourself with claws and grace Find your solace within Cause the sirens can't reject all of that meaning The battle within and the constant strife Afraid of losing the thread of my life Cause we all have fear within All that matters girl is how you deal with it Cause we all have fear within All that matters girl is how you deal with it Cause yet to feel a glimpse of light Courage whispers right through the night Embrace yourself with claws and grace Find your solace from within Fear in yourself, the untamed within A labyrinth of doubt that starts to spin In the depths of your soul A silent cry, a braid of the night You can't defy the fear The fear within All that matters how you deal with it For none of us can defy it The fear within And all that matters now Matters now is how you deal with it All this fear, all the sirens make me be fear All inside is this good time I've been blocked and I've been called You're crushing me to make me Shiny and perfect baby sirens in my mind Listen they will just turn off and let you be alone Oh I wish I was you",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 12.0600004196167,
      "text": "All I fear, all I fear, all I knew inside my own little dream",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 20.139999389648438,
      "text": "In the mirror's gaze, a haunting sight Reflections of the whispers of a dead night",
      "start": 12.0600004196167
    },
    {
      "end": 26.239999771118164,
      "text": "Fear of, fear of myself, fear of myself",
      "start": 20.139999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 32.959999084472656,
      "text": "Yeah, the mask once tied to hide the truth Unraveling thoughts lost in my youth",
      "start": 26.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 40.02000045776367,
      "text": "The battle within and the constant strife Afraid of what's been losing my life",
      "start": 32.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 46.29999923706055,
      "text": "Be yourself, the untamed within A labyrinth of doubt that starts to spin",
      "start": 40.02000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 51.7400016784668,
      "text": "In the depths of your soul A silent cry makes you grow",
      "start": 46.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 66,
      "text": "Cause fear is in us all You gotta work past it as you grow old",
      "start": 52.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 78.73999786376953,
      "text": "My friend, we've all felt this way We all deal with it in our own way",
      "start": 66
    },
    {
      "end": 86.22000122070312,
      "text": "Cause the sirens keep going off inside our minds",
      "start": 78.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 91.73999786376953,
      "text": "Embrace yourself with claws and grace Find your solace within",
      "start": 86.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 98.73999786376953,
      "text": "Cause the sirens can't reject all of that meaning",
      "start": 92.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 107.93000030517578,
      "text": "The battle within and the constant strife Afraid of losing the thread of my life",
      "start": 99.11000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 118.2300033569336,
      "text": "Cause we all have fear within All that matters girl is how you deal with it",
      "start": 107.93000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 132.6300048828125,
      "text": "Cause we all have fear within All that matters girl is how you deal with it",
      "start": 119.2300033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 139.6699981689453,
      "text": "Cause yet to feel a glimpse of light Courage whispers right through the night",
      "start": 132.6300048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 145.49000549316406,
      "text": "Embrace yourself with claws and grace Find your solace from within",
      "start": 139.6699981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 153.00999450683594,
      "text": "Fear in yourself, the untamed within A labyrinth of doubt that starts to spin",
      "start": 146.49000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 158.49000549316406,
      "text": "In the depths of your soul A silent cry, a braid of the night",
      "start": 153.00999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 168.4499969482422,
      "text": "You can't defy the fear The fear within",
      "start": 159.1300048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 171.8699951171875,
      "text": "All that matters how you deal with it",
      "start": 169.4499969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 177.91000366210938,
      "text": "For none of us can defy it The fear within",
      "start": 172.4499969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 185.25,
      "text": "And all that matters now Matters now is how you deal with it",
      "start": 179.4499969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 193.85000610351562,
      "text": "All this fear, all the sirens make me be fear All inside is this good time",
      "start": 185.4499969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 199.61000061035156,
      "text": "I've been blocked and I've been called You're crushing me to make me",
      "start": 193.85000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 207.6300048828125,
      "text": "Shiny and perfect baby sirens in my mind Listen they will just turn off and let you be alone",
      "start": 199.7100067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 211.50999450683594,
      "text": "Oh I wish I was you",
      "start": 208.08999633789062
    }
  ],
